title: Windows.7.AIO.SP1.x64-EN-Unmodified.iso
description:
This release has Service Pack 1 integrated on every edition of Windows 7 and strictly the service pack 1 is integrated and nothing else.

Windows 7 7601 x64 AIO English-US Release
-----------------------------------------
Home Basic - Works
Home Premium - Works
Professional - Works
Enterprise - Works
Ultimate - Works

As you can see every edition works with service pack 1 integrated and nothing else, if you want other features like Internet Explorer, Adobe Flash Player, Net Framework integrated you can download this ISO here and integrate these addons yourself and recompile the ISO the way you want it or look elsewhere that has it.

This is an unmodified version of the ISO which has service pack 1 integrated on every edition and has been tested using VMWare and Actual Machine.

Leave Feedback if you think this works or report any problems you may experience with the image itself.
